No, Jimmy!

1424
02:08:54,812 --> 02:08:57,517
Leave him alone!

1425
02:08:57,581 --> 02:09:01,684
Stay away from him! That aint laying back!

1426
02:09:01,752 --> 02:09:05,026
Braddocks corner is yelling at him
to stay away from Baer,

1427
02:09:05,089 --> 02:09:06,623
whos looking for the knockout.

1428
02:09:06,690 --> 02:09:08,725
Stay off him, Jim. Come on.

1429
02:09:11,529 --> 02:09:13,098
Right hand, Max!

1430
02:09:21,005 --> 02:09:23,449
What is he, stupid?

1431
02:09:25,676 --> 02:09:27,915
Step away, step away!

1432
02:09:27,978 --> 02:09:30,319
trying to survive this brutal onslaught.

1433
02:09:30,381 --> 02:09:33,018
Stay off him!

1434
02:09:35,119 --> 02:09:37,688
Looking good, Maxie!

1435
02:09:41,792 --> 02:09:44,168
Thats the uppercut.
Stay the hell away from it.

1436
02:09:44,228 --> 02:09:47,331
Baer cutting loose with thunderous shots.

1437
02:09:47,398 --> 02:09:49,774
A left to the body.
Baer, again with the right.

1438
02:09:50,201 --> 02:09:52,804
Braddock covering up, trying to hang on.

1439
02:09:53,737 --> 02:09:58,011
Baer looking for the knockout. He doesnt
want this one to go to the cards, folks.

1440
02:09:58,075 --> 02:10:00,314
They pound each other with lefts and rights.

1441
02:10:00,377 --> 02:10:06,219
Braddock blocking with his gloves and
elbows. Snaps a big right to Maxies jaw.

1442
02:10:14,291 --> 02:10:17,394
Baer smashes him with a big right.

1443
02:10:24,902 --> 02:10:28,312
Braddock is back on the ropes.

1444
02:11:13,784 --> 02:11:16,785
Braddock lands a crushing right!

1445
02:11:16,854 --> 02:11:21,923
Maxie desperately wants
to keep the crown from slipping away.

1446
02:11:25,629 --> 02:11:27,698
Jesus Christ!

1447
02:11:31,435 --> 02:11:33,970
Stay with him.

1448
02:11:37,908 --> 02:11:40,943
Both fighters are tired.

1449
02:11:49,353 --> 02:11:51,592
Baer is trying wildly for the knockout.

1450
02:11:52,189 --> 02:11:56,758
Jimmy is still standing. And hes not
only standing, hes moving forward.

1451
02:12:08,639 --> 02:12:12,413
This is the finish. Both boys are tired.

1452
02:12:12,476 --> 02:12:16,250
This is not boxing, folks.
This is a walloping ballet.

1453
02:12:20,517 --> 02:12:23,756
- Ten seconds!
- Son of a bitch.

1454
02:12:37,635 --> 02:12:41,045
Theres the bell!
Its over! This fight is over!

1455
02:12:43,073 --> 02:12:45,244
Son of a bitch!

1456
02:12:52,316 --> 02:12:55,487
What a fight! Unbelievable!

1457
02:12:59,156 --> 02:13:03,623
Braddock came into this fight
the biggest underdog in pugilistic history.

1458
02:13:03,694 --> 02:13:06,035
For 15 rounds
he gave it everything he had

1459
02:13:06,096 --> 02:13:08,369
against the younger, stronger champion.

1460
02:13:19,443 --> 02:13:21,546
We are waiting for the decision.

1461
02:13:23,580 --> 02:13:24,580
Its over.

1462
02:13:30,254 --> 02:13:32,891
McAvoy. McAvoy.

1463
02:13:33,324 --> 02:13:36,063
- What?
- Help me out. Howd you score the fight?

1464
02:13:36,126 --> 02:13:39,331
- Nine-five, one even.
- Which way?

1465
02:13:39,897 --> 02:13:43,171
- You have to read it in the papers, Sporty.
- No, come on!

1466
02:13:45,569 --> 02:13:48,376
What the hell is this crap?

1467
02:13:50,941 --> 02:13:55,408
They take this long to make a decision,
theyre gonna decide to screw someone.

1468
02:13:56,647 --> 02:14:00,091
- Make a decision!
- Theyre gonna rob this poor bastard.

1469
02:14:00,150 --> 02:14:02,526
Unbelievable bullshit.

1470
02:14:08,926 --> 02:14:11,927
Come on, make a decision here!

1471
02:14:15,299 --> 02:14:19,505
The crowd, on its feet for almost
the entire fight, is still standing,

1472
02:14:19,570 --> 02:14:24,037
yelling for who they clearly believe
to be the winner of this fight.

1473
02:14:25,008 --> 02:14:28,748
Well have to wait and see
how the judges scored it.

1474
02:14:45,829 --> 02:14:48,500
Ladies and gentlemen,

1475
02:14:48,565 --> 02:14:51,270
we have your decision.

1476
02:14:52,336 --> 02:14:54,575
Its unanimous.

1477
02:14:54,638 --> 02:14:59,139
Winner and the new world champion,

1478
02:15:00,477 --> 02:15:03,751
James J. Braddock!

1479
02:15:19,563 --> 02:15:21,336
You son of a bitch.

1480
02:15:21,398 --> 02:15:24,137
Jim Braddock has defeated Max Baer

1481
02:15:24,201 --> 02:15:27,179
for the heavyweight championship
of the world!

1482
02:15:29,506 --> 02:15:32,007
He won!

1483
02:15:48,008 --> 02:15:50,508
You earned it.
Hell of a fight.